    "Any ePassport with the chip symbol on the cover (most passports issued since around 2010).": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "أي جواز سفر إلكتروني يحمل رمز الشريحة على الغلاف (معظم جوازات السفر الصادرة منذ حوالي 2010)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "任何封面带有芯片符号的电子护照（大多数自 2010 年左右起签发的护照）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Any single enrolled device unlocks the Identity Sandwich; you don't need all of them. The wrap key never leaves the device.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "أي جهاز مسجَّل واحد يفتح Identity Sandwich؛ لست بحاجة إليها جميعًا. مفتاح التغليف لا يغادر الجهاز أبدًا."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "任何一个已注册的设备都可解锁 Identity Sandwich；您无需全部设备。封装密钥绝不会离开设备。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Any single enrolled device unlocks your wallet; you don't need all of them. The wrap key never leaves the device.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "أي جهاز مسجّل واحد يفتح محفظتك؛ لست بحاجة إليها جميعاً. مفتاح التغليف لا يغادر الجهاز أبداً."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "任何一台已注册的设备都可解锁您的钱包，无需全部设备。封装密钥绝不会离开设备。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Any valid Bitcoin address. Works on mainnet, testnet3, and signet, the address itself encodes which.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "أي عنوان Bitcoin صالح. يعمل على mainnet وtestnet3 وsignet، والعنوان نفسه يحدد أيها."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "任何有效的 Bitcoin 地址。适用于 mainnet、testnet3 和 signet，地址本身即编码了所属网络。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Anything sent will arrive in this wallet.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "أي شيء يُرسَل سيصل إلى هذه المحفظة."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "任何发送的内容都将到达此钱包。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "App": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "التطبيق"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "App"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "应用"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Approve": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "الموافقة"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "批准"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Approve signs these attributes and sends them to the verifier over the network. Your keys never leave this device.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "تؤدي الموافقة إلى توقيع هذه السمات وإرسالها إلى جهة التحقق عبر الشبكة. مفاتيحك لا تغادر هذا الجهاز أبدًا."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "批准将对这些属性进行签名，并通过网络发送给验证方。您的密钥绝不会离开此设备。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Approve the wrap signature on your Trezor's touchscreen. Times out after ~30s of no input.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
