    "During onboarding you set a passphrase. It is NOT shown here. Make sure it is backed up in your password manager (1Password, Bitwarden, iCloud Keychain), kept separate from this 24-word phrase. Without BOTH the phrase and the passphrase, the wallet cannot be recovered.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "أثناء الإعداد قمت بتعيين عبارة مرور. لا تُعرض هنا. تأكد من نسخها احتياطياً في مدير كلمات المرور (1Password، Bitwarden، iCloud Keychain) وحفظها منفصلة عن هذه العبارة المكونة من 24 كلمة. بدون كليهما (العبارة وعبارة المرور)، لا يمكن استرداد المحفظة."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "During onboarding you set a passphrase. It is NOT shown here. Make sure it is backed up in your password manager (1Password, Bitwarden, iCloud Keychain), kept separate from this 24-word phrase. Without BOTH the phrase and the passphrase, the wallet cannot be recovered."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "您在引导流程中设置了口令短语，此处不会显示。请确保已将其备份在密码管理器中（1Password、Bitwarden、iCloud Keychain），且与这 24 个助记词分开保存。缺少助记词和口令短语中的任意一个，钱包都无法恢复。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ENS Registry has no resolver set for that name. The owner needs to set a public resolver before it can be used.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "سجل ENS لا يحتوي على محلِّل مُعيَّن لهذا الاسم. يجب على المالك تعيين محلِّل عام قبل استخدامه."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "ENS 注册表未为该名称设置解析器。所有者需要先设置公共解析器，然后才能使用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
