    "Even if someone steals your 24 word recovery phrase backup, they cannot recover your identity without the passphrase.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "حتى إذا سرق شخص ما النسخة الاحتياطية لعبارة الاسترداد المكونة من 24 كلمة، لا يستطيع استرداد هويتك بدون عبارة المرور."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Even if someone steals your 24 word recovery phrase backup, they cannot recover your identity without the passphrase."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "即使有人盗走您的 24 个助记词备份，没有口令短语也无法恢复您的身份。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Everything has been wiped. You'll land on the onboarding screen on the next render and can set up a fresh identity from there.": {
