    "If you have the descriptor (wpkh([…]xpub…/0/*)), paste it. SeedSigner's \"Sparrow QR\" export works directly.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "إذا كان لديك الواصف (wpkh([…]xpub…/0/*))، فالصقه. يعمل تصدير \"Sparrow QR\" من SeedSigner مباشرة."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "如果您有描述符 (wpkh([…]xpub…/0/*))，请粘贴它。SeedSigner 的 \"Sparrow QR\" 导出可直接使用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If you've registered this device before, Maknoon will recognise its serial and just return the existing record without creating a duplicate.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "إذا كنت قد سجّلت هذا الجهاز من قبل، فسيتعرف Maknoon على رقمه التسلسلي ويعيد السجل الموجود دون إنشاء نسخة مكررة."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If you've registered this device before, Maknoon will recognise its serial and just return the existing record without creating a duplicate."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "如果您之前已注册过此设备，Maknoon 会识别其序列号并直接返回已有记录，不会重复创建。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your chain has an Etherscan-style or Blockscout API, paste the base URL here. Leave blank to fall back to RPC-only history.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "إذا كانت سلسلتك تحتوي على واجهة API بنمط Etherscan أو Blockscout، الصق عنوان URL الأساسي هنا. اتركه فارغاً للرجوع إلى السجل عبر RPC فقط."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "If your chain has an Etherscan-style or Blockscout API, paste the base URL here. Leave blank to fall back to RPC-only history."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "如果您的链提供 Etherscan 风格或 Blockscout 类 API，请在此粘贴基础 URL。留空则仅使用 RPC 读取历史记录。"
          }
        }
