        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "يصل دعم Lightning كتكامل بحراسة مع مزود خارجي (Strike، Wallet of Satoshi، أو ما شابه). لن يشغّل Maknoon عقدة Lightning غير محروسة على الجهاز."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lightning support lands as a custodial integration with a third-party provider (Strike, Wallet of Satoshi, similar). Maknoon will not run a non-custodial Lightning node on-device."
