    "Most Etherscan-family endpoints serve unkeyed traffic at a low rate cap. Heavy users add a free API key from etherscan.io / arbiscan.io / etc.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "معظم نقاط نهاية عائلة Etherscan تخدم حركة المرور بدون مفتاح بحد معدل منخفض. يضيف المستخدمون الكثيفون مفتاح API مجاني من etherscan.io / arbiscan.io / إلخ."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Most Etherscan-family endpoints serve unkeyed traffic at a low rate cap. Heavy users add a free API key from etherscan.io / arbiscan.io / etc."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "大多数 Etherscan 系列端点对无密钥流量设有较低的速率限制。高频用户可在 etherscan.io、arbiscan.io 等站点申请免费 API 密钥。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Move slowly until the phone finds the chip. The bottom of an iPhone reads best.": {
