          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "此版本禁用了 NFC YubiKey 扫描功能，因其需要付费的 Apple Developer Program。USB-C 可在免费的 Personal Team 下使用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "NFC reading isn't available on this device. You can still fill in the details, but the scan step will not work here.": {
