    "Paste the signed PSBT base64 from your signer, or tap Scan QR to capture an animated UR-PSBT (SeedSigner) or single-frame base64 QR (Sparrow / Specter). Maknoon finalizes the signatures with BDK and broadcasts via the configured Electrum endpoint.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "الصق PSBT الموقع بصيغة base64 من موقّعك، أو اضغط فحص QR لالتقاط UR-PSBT متحرك (SeedSigner) أو رمز QR أحادي الإطار بصيغة base64 (Sparrow / Specter). يكمل Maknoon التوقيعات باستخدام BDK ويبثها عبر نقطة نهاية Electrum المكوّنة."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Paste the signed PSBT base64 from your signer, or tap Scan QR to capture an animated UR-PSBT (SeedSigner) or single-frame base64 QR (Sparrow / Specter). Maknoon finalizes the signatures with BDK and broadcasts via the configured Electrum endpoint."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "粘贴签名设备产生的已签名 PSBT base64，或点击“扫描二维码”以捕获动态 UR-PSBT（SeedSigner）或单帧 base64 二维码（Sparrow / Specter）。Maknoon 使用 BDK 完成最终签名，并通过配置的 Electrum 端点广播。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pastes a single line you can append to `swift run ledger-ble-test --psbt-file ...`.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
