    "Static QR. Anyone with this code can confirm the credential exists and is anchored on chain, but cannot read your personal information from it.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "رمز QR ثابت. يمكن لأي شخص يمتلك هذا الرمز تأكيد وجود بيانات الاعتماد وأنها مثبتة على السلسلة، لكنه لا يستطيع قراءة معلوماتك الشخصية منه."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Static QR. Anyone with this code can confirm the credential exists and is anchored on chain, but cannot read your personal information from it."
          }
