    "Take this base64 (or the QR) to your signing device. Sparrow / Trezor Suite / Ledger Live / Specter all accept BIP174 PSBT. The signer adds signatures and gives you back a signed PSBT.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "خذ هذا الـ base64 (أو رمز QR) إلى جهاز التوقيع الخاص بك. Sparrow / Trezor Suite / Ledger Live / Specter جميعها تقبل BIP174 PSBT. يضيف الموقّع التوقيعات ويعيد إليك PSBT موقعاً."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Take this base64 (or the QR) to your signing device. Sparrow / Trezor Suite / Ledger Live / Specter all accept BIP174 PSBT. The signer adds signatures and gives you back a signed PSBT."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "将此 base64（或二维码）传给您的签名设备。Sparrow / Trezor Suite / Ledger Live / Specter 均接受 BIP174 PSBT。签名设备会添加签名并返回已签名的 PSBT。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap + to browse the configured appstores. Default catalog is Elabify-curated; add other institution-curated stores in Settings > Apps.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "اضغط + لتصفح متاجر التطبيقات المكوّنة. الكتالوج الافتراضي منسّق من Elabify، أضف متاجر منسّقة من مؤسسات أخرى من الإعدادات > التطبيقات."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap + to browse the configured appstores. Default catalog is Elabify-curated; add other institution-curated stores in Settings > Apps."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "点击 + 浏览已配置的应用商店。默认目录由 Elabify 精选；在“设置 > 应用”中可添加其他机构精选商店。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap + to paste a contract address. The app reads the symbol and decimals from-chain.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "اضغط + للصق عنوان عقد. يقرأ التطبيق الرمز والمنازل العشرية من السلسلة."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap + to paste a contract address. The app reads the symbol and decimals from-chain."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "点击 + 粘贴合约地址。应用会从链上读取代币符号和小数位。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap ID document": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "المس مستند الهوية"
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap ID document"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "贴近证件"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap Register device to identify a YubiKey or Ledger. Adding it to Identity or to a specific network is a separate step from the device's detail screen.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "انقر على تسجيل الجهاز للتعرّف على YubiKey أو Ledger. أما إضافته إلى الهوية أو إلى شبكة محددة فهي خطوة منفصلة من شاشة تفاصيل الجهاز."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "点按注册设备以识别 YubiKey 或 Ledger。将其添加到身份或特定网络是从设备详情屏幕进行的单独步骤。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap Register device to identify a YubiKey, Ledger, or Trezor. Adding it to Identity or to a specific network is a separate step from the device's detail screen.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "اضغط تسجيل جهاز لتحديد YubiKey أو Ledger أو Trezor. إضافته إلى الهوية أو إلى شبكة محددة هي خطوة منفصلة من شاشة تفاصيل الجهاز."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap Register device to identify a YubiKey, Ledger, or Trezor. Adding it to Identity or to a specific network is a separate step from the device's detail screen."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "点击“注册设备”以识别 YubiKey、Ledger 或 Trezor。将其添加到身份或特定网络是设备详情页上的另一步操作。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap a credential to review what you'll share, then sign + send.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "اضغط على بيانات اعتماد لمراجعة ما ستشاركه، ثم وقّع + أرسل."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap a credential to review what you'll share, then sign + send."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "点击一个凭据查看将要分享的内容，然后签名并发送。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap a device to derive a watch-only wallet from it at a chosen BIP44 account index. Sending routes back to the same device for SIGN_TRANSACTION.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "اضغط على جهاز لاشتقاق محفظة للمراقبة فقط منه عند فهرس حساب BIP44 المختار. يعود الإرسال إلى نفس الجهاز لـ SIGN_TRANSACTION."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap a device to derive a watch-only wallet from it at a chosen BIP44 account index. Sending routes back to the same device for SIGN_TRANSACTION."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "点击设备，从其指定的 BIP44 账户索引派生一个仅观察钱包。发送时会回到同一设备执行 SIGN_TRANSACTION。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the + in the top right to browse the Elabify-curated appstore (and any institution-curated stores you have added in Settings > Apps).": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "اضغط على + في أعلى اليمين لتصفح متجر التطبيقات المنسّق من Elabify (وأي متاجر منسّقة من مؤسسات أضفتها في الإعدادات > التطبيقات)."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap the + in the top right to browse the Elabify-curated appstore (and any institution-curated stores you have added in Settings > Apps)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "点击右上角的 + 浏览 Elabify 精选应用商店（以及您在“设置 > 应用”中添加的任何机构精选商店）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the + in the top right to browse the Maknoon Apps catalog (and any catalogs you have added in Settings > Apps).": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "انقر على علامة + في أعلى اليمين لتصفّح كتالوج تطبيقات Maknoon (وأي كتالوجات أضفتها في الإعدادات > التطبيقات)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "点按右上角的 + 以浏览 Maknoon 应用目录（以及您在设置 > 应用中添加的任何目录）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap the grid to reveal. Tap again to hide before walking away or screen-sharing.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "اضغط على الشبكة للكشف. اضغط مرة أخرى للإخفاء قبل الابتعاد أو مشاركة الشاشة."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Tap the grid to reveal. Tap again to hide before walking away or screen-sharing."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "点击网格显示。在离开或进行屏幕共享前，请再次点击隐藏。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap with NFC to add": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "المس باستخدام NFC للإضافة"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "用 NFC 轻触以添加"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Tap your passport and Maknoon reads its chip on-device and mints an identity credential signed by your post-quantum key, that you can present from your phone. Nothing is uploaded unless you then choose an Elabify-verified credential.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "اضغط جواز سفرك ويقرأ Maknoon شريحته على الجهاز ويصكّ بيانات اعتماد هوية موقّعة بمفتاحك ما بعد الكمي، يمكنك تقديمها من هاتفك. لا يُرفع أي شيء ما لم تختر بعد ذلك بيانات اعتماد مُتحقَّقًا منها عبر Elabify."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "轻触您的护照，Maknoon 会在设备上读取其芯片，并铸造一份由您的后量子密钥签名的身份凭证，您可以从手机出示它。除非您随后选择 Elabify 验证的凭证，否则不会上传任何内容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Testnet": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "شبكة الاختبار"
