    "Unlock your Ledger and open the Ethereum app. Tap Continue when ready.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "افتح قفل Ledger وافتح تطبيق Ethereum. انقر على متابعة عندما تكون جاهزاً."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "解锁您的 Ledger 并打开 Ethereum 应用。准备就绪后点击“继续”。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unlock your Ledger and open the Solana app. The device should show the SOL home screen. Tap Continue when ready.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "افتح قفل Ledger وافتح تطبيق Solana. ينبغي أن يعرض الجهاز شاشة SOL الرئيسية. انقر على متابعة عندما تكون جاهزاً."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "解锁您的 Ledger 并打开 Solana 应用。设备应显示 SOL 主屏幕。准备就绪后点击“继续”。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unlock your Ledger and open the Tron app. The device should show the TRX home screen. Tap Continue when ready.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "افتح قفل Ledger وافتح تطبيق Tron. ينبغي أن يعرض الجهاز شاشة TRX الرئيسية. انقر على متابعة عندما تكون جاهزاً."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "解锁您的 Ledger 并打开 Tron 应用。设备应显示 TRX 主屏幕。准备就绪后点击“继续”。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unlock your Trezor Safe 5. Maknoon will connect over BLE and read the device's Features payload to obtain its serial. Trezor BLE support is still being wired; this step currently returns a not-yet-implemented error.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "افتح قفل Trezor Safe 5 الخاص بك. سيتصل Maknoon عبر BLE ويقرأ حمولة Features للجهاز للحصول على رقمه التسلسلي. لا يزال يجري توصيل دعم Trezor BLE، تُرجع هذه الخطوة حالياً خطأ \"لم يُنفَّذ بعد\"."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Unlock your Trezor Safe 5. Maknoon will connect over BLE and read the device's Features payload to obtain its serial. Trezor BLE support is still being wired; this step currently returns a not-yet-implemented error."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "请解锁您的 Trezor Safe 5。Maknoon 将通过 BLE 连接并读取设备的 Features 数据以获取序列号。Trezor BLE 支持仍在接入中，此步骤当前会返回“尚未实现”错误。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unlock your Trezor so Maknoon can read its serial over Bluetooth.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "افتح قفل Trezor الخاص بك حتى يتمكن Maknoon من قراءة رقمه التسلسلي عبر Bluetooth."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
