    "Verifies a legacy \"Bitcoin Signed Message\" signature (Bitcoin Core / Electrum). Paste the address, message, and base64 signature from any source. Works for legacy addresses (starting with 1 on mainnet).": {
      "localizations": {
        "ar": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "يتحقق من توقيع \"Bitcoin Signed Message\" القديم (Bitcoin Core / Electrum). الصق العنوان والرسالة والتوقيع بصيغة base64 من أي مصدر. يعمل مع العناوين القديمة (التي تبدأ بـ 1 على الشبكة الرئيسية)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "验证传统的\"Bitcoin Signed Message\"签名（Bitcoin Core / Electrum）。从任何来源粘贴地址、消息和 base64 签名。适用于传统地址（主网上以 1 开头）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Verifies a legacy \\\"Bitcoin Signed Message\\\" signature (Bitcoin Core / Electrum). Paste the address, message, and base64 signature from any source. Works for legacy addresses (starting with 1 on mainnet).": {
